title.narrative: Fast Track approach towards ending the AIDS epidemic as public health threat by 2030 achieving 95-95-95 targets

description.narrative: Nepal - HIV - Save the Children Federation, Inc. - STC HQ. This program has the following goals: To accelerate the HIV response prioritized by NHSP to end the AIDS Epidemic by 2030 in Nepal.. The objectives of this program are: Expand access to HIV prevention, treatment, care and support services ensuring the needs of different communities. Improve health outcomes for people living with HIV and key populations. Address stigma and discrimination in partnership with key populations that impede HIV prevention, treatment and care.
